data.title: Southwest Airlines (WN)
data.meta_description: Southwest Airlines is an Airline that provides Air based transport and runs regular services across The United States. The IATA code for Southwest Airlines is WN.
data.text: Southwest Airlines has regular services to the following airports: Denver International Airport, Harry Reid International Airport, Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport, Chicago Midway International Airport, Phoenix Sky Harbor International Airport, Dallas Love Field, William P Hobby Airport, Nashville International Airport, St Louis Lambert International Airport, Orlando International Airport + many more. To see more information on the services and schedules provided by Southwest Airlines, please see our Port Finder and Routing applications.
